  <div class="container feature">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-5">
        <h3 class="feature-title">Start a Group</h3>
        <p class="explain">With a free Start Charlotte account, you can create and manage as many groups as you like. Start a book club, a hiking group, or even a professional organization.</p><br />
        <p class="explain">There are no limits on the the number of members your groups can have, and you can add or invite new members anytime. You can also choose to make your group public or private.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-5 col-sm-offset-1">
        <i class="fa fa-user fa-5x"></i>
        <i class="fa fa-user fa-5x"></i>
        <i class="fa fa-user fa-5x"></i>
        <i class="fa fa-user fa-5x"></i>
        <i class="fa fa-user fa-5x"></i>
