  <!--**********************************************************************-->
  
    <div class="container feature desk">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-5 col-sm-offset-6">
          <div class="backfill">
          <h3 class="feature-title front">Plan Your Event</h3>
            <p class="explain front">Planning any event requires good organization, especially as the size of your event increases.</p>
            <br />
            <p class="explain front">Keep track of each event's details in your group dashboard, including date, location and time. Use the built-in to-do list to keep yourself organized and check off tasks as they are completed to help make your event a success!</p>
        </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
     
  <hr class="custom" />

  <!--**********************************************************************-->

  <div class="container feature">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-5">
        <h3 class="feature-title">Spread the Word</h3>
        <p class="explain">Users can become group members through your group's info page. Then, you can send email reminders of event details, or ask your members to share the link and invite friends to attend as well. Use social media outlets to share sign-up or event info for your group to reach the largest audience.</p>
      </div>
  
      <div class="col-sm-5 col-sm-offset-1">
        <i class="fa fa-envelope-o fa-5x"></i>
        <i class="fa fa-facebook-square fa-5x"></i>
        <i class="fa fa-twitter-square fa-5x"></i>
        <i class="fa fa-google-plus-square fa-5x"></i>
        <i class="fa fa-linkedin-square fa-5x"></i>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
      
  <hr class="custom" />

  <!--**********************************************************************-->

  <div class="container feature rsvp">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-5 col-sm-offset-6">">
        <div class="backfill">
          <h3 class="feature-title front">Manage RSVPs</h3>
            <p class="explain front">As group members register for events, track RSVPs inside your group's dashboard. Members who are attending are listed and color-coded, as are those who RSVP no. You can stay up-to-date on the number of attendees and quickly scan the list for changes.</p>
            <p class="explain front">It is also possible to look back at each event and view the number of attending members, so that you can track which events or types of events were most popular with your members.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="custom" />

  <!--**********************************************************************-->
  
  <div class="container feature">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-5">
        <h3 class="feature-title">Accept Payments Online</h3>
